{"tid":773634,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"見到聽開有個拍本地band live既channel比youtube bam左","createTime":"2018-08-09T16:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T02:31:30.000Z","uid":146887,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1db75530858df4bd5b868aa315cf21eb2e5963","tid":773634,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/002020_982130a8bbe65abfa6f4c093911fb007.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F002020_982130a8bbe65abfa6f4c093911fb007.png&h=1f3d5250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫mouselovekoma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個channel有拍開好多本地band既live show 除左大路既sm kolor 之外連啲地下啲既band都有<br />\n冇啦啦比人bam左真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港地已經好少人會咁有心幫手影live band出show<br />\n真係屌佢個閪 廣告就識落 落到條條片都有 但係咁高汁既channel就bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦呻完 有冇清知同youtube cs反映有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b02ea24edc4b19941a16408d9712d963653e2e9","tid":773634,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:27:24.000Z","msg":"利申 唔係開channel個個 但係真係好鍾意聽本地band既live<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fe4d52d7d3670bbb82049d1a6712c49d3cd1af","tid":773634,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b70751e9c339dc8f2c98ed24e4accb65b96d4e","tid":773634,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"01f8706027c781a087a94c37f6c2a5fa431865fd","tid":773634,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"